2011年1月NBC宣布他们订购了一部名为“{{lang|en|''Grimm''}}”的电视剧试播集<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/01/28/buffy-grimm-nbc/|title='Buffy' writers sell Grimm's Fairy Tales pilot to NBC|last=Hibberd|first=James|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=January 28, 2011|accessdate=July 21, 2011|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216200857/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/01/28/buffy-grimm-nbc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。David Greenwalt和Jim Kouf一同编写试播集的剧本，并由Marc Buckland执导试播集，试播集于同年三月份在俄勒冈州波特兰市拍摄<ref name=oregonian>{{Cite news |url=http://www.oregonlive.com/movies/index.ssf/2011/03/nbc_pilot_grimm_to_shoot_in_po.html |title=NBC pilot, 'Grimm,' to shoot in Portland in March |last=Turnquist |first=Kristi |work=[[The_Oregonian|The Oregonian]] |date=March 1, 2011 |accessdate=July 21, 2011 |archive-date=2018-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181208115613/https://www.oregonlive.com/movies/index.ssf/2011/03/nbc_pilot_grimm_to_shoot_in_po.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年5月NBC正式预订本剧<ref>{{cite news|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/05/12/nbc-picks-up-playboy-and-jason-isaacs-drama/|title=NBC orders 'The Playboy Club,' other pilots to series|last=Rice|first=Lynette|last2=Hibberd|first2=James|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=May 12, 2011|accessdate=July 21, 2011|archive-date=2014-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208074514/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/05/12/nbc-picks-up-playboy-and-jason-isaacs-drama/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

